Hi <%= @name %>,

Thank you for your recent purchase! This email is just to let you know
that your order will be available for pickup at <%= @pickup.location %>
on <%= @pickup.date.strftime("%b %d, %Y") %>
from <%= @pickup.start.strftime("%I:%M %p") %> to <%= @pickup.end.strftime("%I:%M %p") %>.

Remember to have your Stripe receipt ready from when you made your purchase(it will be in your email inbox). 
If you can't make it to the pickup - don't worry! I will keep you up to date on when we can meet up next!

<% if @pickup.details %>
  Additional Details: 
  <%= @pickup.details %>
<% end %>

Paste the link in your browser for a map location of the pickup: <%= @pickup.link %>

See you soon!

Jessie Edwards
Zold Ceramics
https://zoldceramics.com
